Step.SQLStatement: CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW RV_LVE_Fiscal_ChangeLog AS SELECT s.AD_session_ID, s.AD_Client_ID, s.AD_Org_ID, cl.Created, cl.Createdby, cl.Updated, cl.Updatedby, s.WebSession, s.Remote_Addr, s.Remote_Host, s.Processed, s.AD_role_ID, s.LoginDate, cl.AD_ChangeLog_ID, cl.AD_Table_ID, cl.AD_Column_ID, cl.Record_ID, cl.OldValue, cl.NewValue, cl.EventChangeLog, cl.UUID FROM AD_ChangeLog cl JOIN AD_Session s ON (cl.AD_session_ID = s.AD_session_ID) LEFT JOIN C_Invoice i ON (cl.Record_ID = i.C_Invoice_ID AND cl.AD_Table_ID = 318) LEFT JOIN C_Order o ON (cl.Record_ID = o.C_Order_ID AND cl.AD_Table_ID = 259) LEFT JOIN M_InOut io ON (cl.Record_ID = io.M_Inout_ID AND cl.AD_Table_ID = 319) LEFT JOIN M_Movement m ON (cl.Record_ID = m.M_Movement_ID AND cl.AD_Table_ID = 323) LEFT JOIN ( SELECT s.AD_sequence_ID, dt.IsFiscalDocument FROM AD_sequence s, c_doctype dt WHERE dt.IsFiscalDocument = 'Y' AND (s.AD_Sequence_ID = COALESCE(dt.DocNoSequence_ID, 0) OR s.AD_Sequence_ID = COALESCE(dt.DefiniteSequence_ID, 0) OR s.AD_Sequence_ID = COALESCE(dt.ControlNoSequence_ID, 0))) seq ON cl.Record_ID = seq.AD_Sequence_ID AND cl.AD_Table_ID = 115 WHERE cl.AD_Table_ID IN (323, 319, 318, 259, 115) AND COALESCE(i.IsFiscalDocument, o.IsFiscalDocument, seq.IsFiscalDocument, io.IsFiscalDocument, m.IsFiscalDocument) = 'Y';
